doc.title: Akopọ ti Ọna asopọ Ṣii Pẹlu itẹsiwaju
doc.description:
Afikun yii gba ọ laaye lati ṣakoso ni irọrun bi awọn ọna asopọ hyperlinks ṣe ṣii.

Fèrèse: awọn aṣawakiri miiran, awọn window agbejade, awọn window tuntun, awọn window incognito tuntun, window lọwọlọwọ (aiyipada)

Awọn taabu: osi ti lọwọlọwọ taabu, lọwọlọwọ taabu, ọtun ti lọwọlọwọ taabu (aiyipada)

Ipo imuṣiṣẹ: aiṣiṣẹ, mu ṣiṣẹ lẹsẹkẹsẹ (aiyipada)
